{"tid":592788,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"某國人大： 涉案人被留置扣押時律師不得介入","createTime":"2018-03-14T13:17:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T23:49:17.000Z","uid":72155,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9916571cb1af38e8f1aa6387760c27c59e79292a","tid":592788,"uid":72155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T13:17:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1663126060498540/?t=87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F1663126060498540%2F%3Ft%3D87&d=8aBMm4NG%2BqopGMwwVxN5qGMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=3010362a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1663126060498540/?t=87</a><br />\n<br />\n【《國家監察法草案》提交審議】<br />\n【涉案人被留置扣押時律師不得介入】<br />\n<br />\n《國家監察法草案》提交到全國人大審議，草案規定即將成立的監察委員會獨立行使監察權，不受行政機關、社會團體和個人干涉，調查貪污賄賂、濫用職權等違法行為。<br />\n<br />\n委員會要監察的對象非常廣泛：上至中共機關、人大、政協、法院、檢察院；下至國企管理人員、公辦學校及醫院等的管理層，涵蓋所有公職人員。<br />\n<br />\n全國人大副委員長李建國指，制定監察法是要加強黨對反腐敗工作的集中統一領導。<br />\n<br />\n另外草案又寫明，監察機關可採取談話、詢問、凍結、扣押等12種調查措施。當中最受關注的是取代「雙規」的「留置」措施。規定在案情嚴重，涉案人可能自殺、逃跑等的情況下，可以把涉案人「留置」在特定場所，時間一般不超過三個月，特殊情況可延長至最多半年。<br />\n<br />\n外界關注留置期間律師可否介入協助。有地方試點的監察委主任指律師介入只存在於《刑事訴訟法》，不適用於監察委。<br />\n<br />\n#國家監察法<br />\n#反腐<br />\n#黨的集中統一領導<br />\n#留置<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n習帝的依法治國- 律師都唔俾你見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9b32154db482755c8bf1e05b4e9ccd33da4c546","tid":592788,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T13:18:52.000Z","msg":"以為講緊台灣殺人果條mk <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec3a61cca7adfe04ba7798133649fdaf3ec737b","tid":592788,"uid":83251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T13:18:55.000Z","msg":"東廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb83c70dec100279110552e56b7873b6e54a374c","tid":592788,"uid":50457,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T23:25:04.000Z","msg":"東廠復活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"592f8d50009118b05230063bcac16d01a53a5313","tid":592788,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T23:35:05.000Z","msg":"依法喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依你個老母閪法<br />\n真係無法無天"},{"pid":"3aade261b31e75c57bd5f96d3864b54b81521b4e","tid":592788,"uid":69924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T23:37:12.000Z","msg":"錦衣衛 操生殺大權"},{"pid":"5b538bb4b8a3ed5d008182d429c63da5f215f5a4","tid":592788,"uid":50457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T23:44:31.000Z","msg":"單獨問話，又比你睇下老婆仔女的相<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n認唔認罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9559a5356c04ecdfa4f773505e033b8e88e7eca4","tid":592788,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T23:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> mk單案都成班小學雞話辯方律師無公義"}]}